  <activityInformation><![CDATA[<p><strong><span style="color: #00533a;">Spas<br /></span></strong></p>
<p>Hotel Beatus set on the bank of Lake Thun is known for it's excellent wellness facilities which provide a front-row seat to the trappings of the lake. Indoor pool, saltwater pool and saunas are just a few facilities this hotel provides.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Lake Thun is also famous for:</p>
<ul>
<li>The ‘Strämu’, Switzerland’s largest outdoor swimming pool</li>
<li>Nearly 1,000 shops</li>
<li>Visit Interlaken and nearby Lake Brienz</li>
</ul>]]></activityInformation>
